{"tid":1897261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一直屌陳秋實支持武統台灣個班無腦兒登狗其實有無睇過條片","createTime":"2020-02-25T15:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T00:02:32.000Z","uid":288670,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e09a2b773b80e017d903500de8f4813474fe58b","tid":1897261,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NxMeXCATFxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNxMeXCATFxo&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWD%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=2c34ddba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NxMeXCATFxo</a><br />\n<br />\n你班垃圾由1:08:30開始睇下 用下你地個豬腦自己去諗諗啦<br />\n<br />\n根本好多兒登狗都好鍾意人云亦云 睇過陳秋實原片都知佢個原意根本就屌緊個班鍾意大一統既五毛蛆<br />\n不過兒登狗們見到佢地尊敬既五毛大大都一齊屌陳秋實支持武統台灣 兒登狗們就一齊屌陳秋實 兒登狗真係狗一樣 無腦又對五毛夠忠誠"},{"pid":"73cde209df5869f67cff2e8f8be75075016e87a0","tid":1897261,"uid":83128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:32:46.000Z","msg":"連登唔會理陳秋實"},{"pid":"eb732b8364385f2d35f98e1cf7defbb448e61cf0","tid":1897261,"uid":201512,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"陳秋實體制內宣傳器勿推"},{"pid":"129930ca614dee2a3eb017f239f79a110e3b5907","tid":1897261,"uid":209248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T01:00:53.000Z","msg":"好撚煩 邊個得閒理佢"},{"pid":"32221b4f93611ac382cdb80df781f03c31ae07cb","tid":1897261,"uid":275475,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yu4ObGU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYu4ObGU.png&h=261de0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0suynOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0suynOt.png&h=5b5215d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QBPKutw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQBPKutw.png&h=9d5e32e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bc449efeefa